  SERVICES OFFERED<br />
  OASIS' services are for registered users. A visitor can only view the main page of the website. <br />
  Through OASIS, a Parent/Guardian can monitor a student's (academic) information online. In OASIS, a registered Parent/Guardian will be known as a &quot;follower&quot; or &quot;user&quot; and the Student he follows will be known as his/her &quot;ward&quot;. <br />
  A Follower can follow a Ward, in other words a follower:<br />
  1.	Can view a Ward's profile, grades, checklist, and schedule. <br />
  2.	Will be notified of dropped class cards, shifting, checklist updates, grade updates, and violations.<br />
  3.	Can monitor Student's Tuition Fee, Balances and Payments.<br />
