<p>REGISTRATION <br />
  Without a Ward, there is no Follower. This means that to register, a Parent or Guardian must have a student/s to monitor.  To monitor student/s, a Parent or Guardian must know a Student's Student Verification Code (SVC).  SVCs are generated by OASIS for every enrolled student who does not yet exist in the OASIS database. The only way to obtain an SVC is through the Verification Letter (VL).  The VL is an invitation to Parents or Guardians for OASIS registration. A VL contains the Student's information (Name, ID number and SVC), Registration Instructions, Registration Period. VLs are sent to students' home addresses or requested directly at the OASIS Admin Office.<br />
  <br /> 
  For Parents or Guardians of SLU Students who did not receive a VL or their VL's content has incomplete information, they can contact the OASIS Admin. <br />
  <br />
  A Follower can have more than one Ward. Therefore the number of VL sent to a home address depends upon the number of newly activated wards with that home address.</p>
<p>OASIS Admin and SLU do not require Parents or Guardians of SLU Students to register in the OASIS. The OASIS Registration Letter is merely an invitation. </p>
<p>Security of the VL's content will no longer be the responsibility of the OASIS Admin after it has been sent to the Student's Home Address.</p>
<p>A Ward can have more than one follower, therefore a Parent or Guardian is responsible for any registration using a ward's SVC. The OASIS Administrator and User Administrator can block a user with/without a Parent or Guardian's complaint. </p>
<p>OASIS registration opens every semester only accepting registration of users that have active ward/s to follow and can provide that Ward's active SVC. Registration period is usually 30 days starting from the 3rd week after enrolment. The SVC will also expire after the registration period. If parents or guardians missed the registration period, they may request for an SVC at the OASIS Admin Office. If the request passed the OASIS Administrator's evaluation, OASIS Admin will generate a new SVC for the specified Ward and reactivate the registration. </p>
